----------------------------------------------
Chapter 0 - 	About PI
----------------------------------------------

PI is a software designed to calculus pi.

----------------------------------------------
Chapter 1 - 	Install
----------------------------------------------

1.1 Required software
A up-to-date Perl compiler and sqlite version 3.x.x.

1.2 Required packages
A list of Perl packages used:
    warnings
    strict
    IO::Socket
    Proc::Daemon (not required if don't launched as daemon)
    Math::BigFloat
    Log::Log4perl
    Data::Dumper (required only to debug)
    Storable
    DBI
    DateTime
	
1.3 DB structure
    Please watch the schema/ directory

1.4 inc/log*.conf
    In these files, you can change many configuration settings to log

